  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK Note Verbale 197/20 logged with UN Treaty Section
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">UK Note Verbale 12 Oct 2020 on continued extension of the 1994 Agreement relating to the implementation of Part XI of UNCLOS to BIOT</p>

  </div>
</div>

